description:
Dave East is back for part two on Lip Service with Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire and Lore'l. The ladies mention his latest single "Perfect" featuring Chris Brown and try to figure out what his perfect girl is. They also discuss how fame has changed his life, oral with a condom on, giving every girl the same type of sex, how your Uber ride determines how good your sex is, the Christina Milian pictures on the internet and how dealing with multiple girls gets tricky which sometimes makes him miss dealing with one p
